   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="Kerr_2487_002_01_R"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb415">Aussee</rs></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1900-07-30">30/7 900</date>.</dateline></opener><p><salute>Mein lieber Paul,</salute> wir (<rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Richard</rs> u. ich) haben <date when="1900-07-30">heute</date>
                  folgend<unclear>e</unclear> Punkte fe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tgestellt:</p><p><date when="1900-08-12">So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag 12.</date> Rendezvous <hi rend="underline" n="1"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs></hi> (<rs type="place" ref="#pmb230">Oe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>terr. Hof</rs>.)</p><p><date when="1900-08-13">13.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs>.</p><p><date when="1900-08-14">14.</date> Nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40336">Zell am
                  See</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90148">Mo<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>erboden</rs></p><p><date when="1900-08-15">15.</date> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90148">Mo<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>erboden</rs>
               – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40336">Zell am See</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb867"><hi rend="underline" n="2">Innsbruck</hi></rs></p><p><date when="1900-08-16">16.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb867">Innsbruck</rs> Bahn <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90366">Bludenz</rs> Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <rs type="place" ref="#pmb38711">Schruns</rs>.</p><p><pb facs="Kerr_2487_002_02_L"/><date when="1900-08-17">17.</date>, event. <date when="1900-08-18">18.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb38711">Schruns</rs>. –</p><p><date when="1900-08-19">19.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb38711">Schruns</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb144646">Sulzfluh</rs></p><p><date when="1900-08-20">20.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="7"/>– <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40646">Küblis</rs></p><p><date when="1900-08-21">21.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1900-08-22">22.</date> auf einen noch nicht be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ti<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>ten Weg nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34946">Pontre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ina</rs>.</p><p>Von dort nach Übereinko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en <add place="inline">1)</add>
               entweder <rs type="place" ref="#pmb49343">Bormio</rs>, <add place="above">a)</add>
               von <rs type="place" ref="#pmb49343">Bormio</rs> gegen <rs type="place" ref="#pmb91918">Trafoi</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb91855">Sulden</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="latintype">etc</hi> b) von <rs type="place" ref="#pmb49343">Bormio</rs>
               nach dem <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb142872">Lago d’Iseo</rs></hi> oder 2) von <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34946">Pontre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ina</rs> we<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tlich in die
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43435">Schweiz</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><pb facs="Kerr_2487_002_02_R"/>oder 3) von <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34946">Pontre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ina</rs> nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40306">Italien</rs>. –</p><p>Am<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten wäre al<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o, <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03176-1"/>we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> Du am <date when="1900-08-12">12.</date> od. <date when="1900-08-13">13.</date> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs>
                  einträf<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03176-1"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L02920" subtype="See"/>.
               </note>; we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> Dir das nicht möglich am <date when="1900-08-15">15.</date> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb867">Innsbruck</rs>. –</p><p>Vielleicht <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03176-2"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ende<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Brief gleich an <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11910">Kerr</rs></hi><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03176-2">Das geschah, er ist im Nachlass <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11910">Kerrs</rs> überliefert.</note>, für den das<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>elbe gilt. Ich wei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s nicht, wohin ich zu adre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>iren hätte.</p><p><pb facs="Kerr_2487_002_01_L"/>Ich fahre <date when="1900-07-31">morgen</date> nach
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb414"><hi rend="underline" n="1">I<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chl, Rudolfshöhe</hi></rs>, wo mich <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03176-3"/>bis auf weiteres<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03176-3"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> reiste am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1900-08-10" subtype="date-only"/> nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs> ab.</note> Nachrichten treffen.</p><p>Bitte um recht baldige Ver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tändg <hi rend="latintype">resp</hi> Einver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tändnis.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <unclear>G</unclear>ruß<lb/>Dein <lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
